  "text": "With such long distance propagation and long lifetime, it is now possible to construct experiments in which two or more beams are used and caused to interact. This could be used to directly measure the polariton-polariton interactions and also for schemes of optical gating using polaritons, as presented e.g. in Ref. [CITATION_1] .",
